{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, data were collected from 25 participants (20 males and 5 females) aged between 18 and 52 years (Mean = 26.8 years, SD = 6.59 years).",
    "The basic physical conditions of the participants were as follows: weight 48-108 kg (Mean = 76.4 kg, SD = 14.6 kg); height 160-190 cm (Mean = 174 cm, SD = 8.33 cm) (Shown in Table 3).",
    "The participants' training experience varied between 0 and 22 years (Mean = 3.96 years, SD = 6.9 years).",
    "All participants demonstrated dominance in one hand and confirmed that they predominantly use this hand in badminton.",
    "Before data collection, the participants were briefed about the use of multiple wearable sensors and agreed to participate in the study."
  ]
}